{"timestamp":"2026-03-14T05:33:38.988Z","level":"WARN","message":"codex stderr","iteration":17,"chunk":"codex\nChanged [loopLogic.ts](/abs/path/c:/Users/ben.jones/source/repos/Ralph/RalphDex/ralph-codex-vscode-starter/src/ralph/loopLogic.ts#L264) so loop stopping now scopes trailing `no_progress` and repeated-failure detection to the current `agentId` as well as `selectedTaskId`. That closes the remaining gap where interleaved history from another agent could still trigger an automatic stop even though remediation counting was already agent-aware. I also added regressions in [loopLogic.test.ts](/abs/path/c:/Users/ben.jones/source/repos/Ralph/RalphDex/ralph-codex-vscode-starter/test/loopLogic.test.ts#L189) and [loopLogic.test.ts](/abs/path/c:/Users/ben.jones/source/repos/Ralph/RalphDex/ralph-codex-vscode-starter/test/loopLogic.test.ts#L237) covering interleaved same-task history for both stop paths.\n\nValidation: `cd ralph-codex-vscode-starter && npm test` still fails in this sandbox with pre-existing `spawn EPERM` errors in process/git-backed tests, but the task-local suite passed with `node --require ./test/register-vscode-stub.cjs --test --test-isolation=none ./out-test/test/loopLogic.test.js` (`17/17` passing).\n\nAssumptions/blockers: I treated the current codebase as partially landed and only finished the remaining stop-decision gap. No functional blocker remains for this task; the only verification limitation is the sandbox preventing some broader integration tests from spawning child processes.\n\nKnown limitations/follow-up: the broader `npm test` failure is environmental rather than caused by this change, so any full-suite confirmation needs a runner that permits the affected spawn paths.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"selectedTaskId\": \"T24.3.2\",\n  \"requestedStatus\": \"done\",\n  \"progressNote\": \"Scoped repeated stop detection in loopLogic.ts to the current agentId for both no-progress and repeated-identical-failure paths, and added regression tests for interleaved multi-agent history on the same task.\",\n  \"validationRan\": true,\n  \"needsHumanReview\": false\n}\n```\n"}
